summary: Completed comprehensive testing of PMC Snag List enhanced web admin dashboard. All core functionality and new features working correctly including building-wise snag numbering, project autocomplete, photo upload buttons, role-based editing, and export functionality.

minor_bugs.endpoint: All protected endpoints with invalid JWT token
minor_bugs.issue: Returns 520 Internal Server Error instead of 401 Unauthorized for invalid JWT tokens
minor_bugs.impact: Minor - doesn't affect functionality but could improve error handling

Manager authentication successful (manager@pmc.com/manager123)
